<div class="section the_content has_content"><div class="section_wrapper"><div class="the_content_wrapper"><h1 style="margin-top: 0;">RN Motors is a local family run business, specializing in MOT and vehicle servicing/repair for over 25 years.</h1>
<p><img class="size-medium wp-image-360 alignleft" src="https://rnmotors.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/header-bg-300x200.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="200" srcset="https://rnmotors.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/header-bg-300x200.jpg 300w, https://rnmotors.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/header-bg-768x512.jpg 768w, https://rnmotors.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/header-bg-219x146.jpg 219w, https://rnmotors.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/header-bg-50x33.jpg 50w, https://rnmotors.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/header-bg-113x75.jpg 113w, https://rnmotors.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/header-bg.jpg 800w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" />RN Motors is a family run business that has been <strong>established for over 25 years</strong> promoting an excellent reputation, renowned for exemplary customer service and high quality of work. Our services include “While you wait” <a href="http://www.rnmotors.co.uk/slides/smart-mots/">MOT’s</a> on vehicles and motorcycles as well as <a href="http://www.rnmotors.co.uk/slides/vehicle-servicing/">servicing</a> and <a href="http://www.rnmotors.co.uk/slides/body-repairs/">repairs</a> on a wide range of vehicles, including the most up to date to vintage.</p>
<p>We encourage our customers to visit the station whilst larger repairs are in progress enabling you the opportunity to view work in progress and discuss elements of work being undertaken should you so wish. We realize however, that it is not always convenient for customers to make such visits and as such offer an up to date progress report at your request.</p>
<p>As part of our continued commitment to providing exemplary customer service, we now offer to photograph and video work in progress showing key stages and send this to our customers on the platform of their choice and at their request.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h1>Additional Extras</h1>
<p>We at RN Motors, are also able to cater for all additional work no matter how large or small, from engine replacements, gearbox’s and clutch kits, to fitting tyres, exhausts and lights.</p>
<p>All work is conducted in a professional manner via our experienced technicians and all work is guaranteed.</p>
<ul>
<li>Pick up and drop off service for local customers.</li>
<li>Free courtesy vehicle dependant on availability.</li>
<li>Free visual brake safety inspection.</li>
<li>Laser wheel alignment.</li>
<li>Air conditioning service from £49.99</li>
<li>Breakdown/Recovery Service: If you have broken down, please contact us and we will arrange for your vehicle to be collected safely and brought to our centre for inspection.</li>
<li>Free levels and tyre pressure check for all old age pensioners.</li>
</ul>
